            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1619444718665-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> potatoes</strong> (skins on) into wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>wedges</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 30 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1619444724077-x200.jpg",
