          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1619444724077-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the leeks are softened, add them to the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs </strong>with the<strong> egg yolk mixture</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Tip: Mix thoroughly until you are left with a mouldable texture</p><p>Divide the mixture into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> and carefully roll into fat sausage shapes – these are your <strong>Glamorgan sausages</strong></p><p>Tip: They don't have to be perfect, but make sure they're packed tightly!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1619444737827-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1619444737827-x400.jpg",
