            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a handful of<strong> flour </strong>to a plate</p><p>Beat the <strong>egg whites</strong> with a fork</p><p>Add the<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong> to another plate</p><p>Coat the<strong> Glamorgan sausages</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add to the<strong> beaten egg whites</strong> and finally press into the <strong>cheese</strong> to evenly coat</p><p>Add to a<strong> baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray and put in the oven for 20 min or until crisp</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
